      <title>津巴布韦公司支撑Zig下的超充电会计</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/-usd-zwg-zimbabwe-companies-risk-hyperinflation-accounting-return-using-zig</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦的市场监管机构正在寻求中央银行对新规则的清晰度，这些规则要求公司报告当地货币的结果，从而迫使他们采用过度通货膨胀会计并增加了经商成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/-usd-zwg-zimbabwe-companies-risk-hyperinflation-accounting-return-using-zig</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 16:32:57 GMT</pubDate>
